e-2000x1270-Scott-Dudelson_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/the-game-2000x1270-Scott-Dudelson_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/the-game-2000x1270-Scott-Dudelson_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/the-game-2000x1270-Scott-Dudelson_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/the-game-2000x1270-Scott-Dudelson_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/the-game">该游戏</a>一直在为消防员提供帮助和物资，以阻止洛杉矶野火的蔓延。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界告诉我们野火的“悲剧性”影响：“这种影响将持续多年”</a></strong></li></ul><p>自 1 月 7 日以来，山火在洛杉矶大都市区爆发并蔓延，造成广泛破坏，特别是在太平洋帕利塞德和阿尔塔迪纳。许多人被迫撤离，而各消防部门和志愿者则试图控制火势。</p><p>截至撰写本文时， <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/live/2025/01/12/us/los-angeles-fires-california" target="_blank" rel="noopener">臭名昭著的洛杉矶大火已夺去了至少 24 人的生命</a>， <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/1/11/firefighters-race-to-contain-la-wildfires-as-winds-expected-to-pick-up" target="_blank" rel="noopener">损坏了超过 12,401 座建筑物，并迫使近 180,000 人撤离家园</a>。</p><p>在洛杉矶出生和长大的说唱歌手 The Game（真名 Jayceon Taylor）分享了<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEv4H4cPire/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">他与帕萨迪纳消防局的照片和视频，</a>并在 Instagram 视频中解释说，他正在分发“毯子、枕头、咖啡、香蕉、水——任何东西”我们可以伸出援助之手来帮助这些消防员。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEv4H4cPire/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="backgr